title: Talkin Bout The Noles! Week 10, Reviewed
description:
An actual discussion about Willie Taggart’s firing at Florida State after just 21 games at the job, everyone wondering what a grown man has to say to get kicked out of the Liberty Bowl, clowning on Nebraska because we can, a brief mention of that whole Georgia-beating-Florida thing in Jacksonville, extended wowing at how bad Arkansas and Chad Morris has gone,  and an appreciation of the only college football stadium that could be a level in Tony Hawk Pro Skater
